      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i hear you, but i don't know if a walk is gonna fix it. it’s more like... if i just stopped showing up... if i just stopped logging in and stopped responding to everything... would anyone even notice? would it even leave a dent, or would everyone just keep typing like nothing happened?",
